<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reset Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f8fa;
      padding: 30px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      background-color: #fff;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #2a2a2a;
    }
    .otp-box {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: #eef1f7;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      display: inline-block;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .timer {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #d9534f;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hai {{name}},</h2>
    <p>Kami menerima permintaan untuk mereset password akun Anda (<strong>{{email}}</strong>).</p>
    
    <p>Gunakan kode OTP berikut untuk melanjutkan proses reset password Anda:</p>

    <div class="otp-box">{{otpToken}}</div>
    <p>or</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="window.location.href='http://localhost:3232/auth/reset-password/{{userId}}/{{otpToken}}'">Reset Password</button>
    
    <p class="timer" id="countdown">Kode akan kadaluarsa dalam <span id="time">30</span> detik.</p>

    <p>Jika Anda tidak meminta reset password, abaikan email ini.</p>

    <footer>
      &copy; {{year}} Sistem Keamanan Kami. Semua hak dilindungi.
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    (function() {
      var timeLeft = 60;
      var countdownEl = document.getElementById('time');
      var interval = setInterval(function() {
        timeLeft--;
        if (timeLeft <= 0) {
          clearInterval(interval);
          document.getElementById('countdown').innerText = 'Kode telah kadaluarsa.';
        } else {
          countdownEl.textContent = timeLeft;
        }
      }, 1000);
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
